    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Okay, I've been debugging this for quite a while now and it seems this is related to the font we're using.\n\nI've noticed that the only items that are disappearing are the ones that have a `font.weight: Font.Medium`.\n\nChanging this to `Font.Normal` or even all to `Font.Bold` causes the flicker to go away.\n\nThere's a chance that maybe there's a QML bug when scaling the font.weight, but I can't say for sure. So one \"solution\" to this would be to switch to `Font.Normal`, but this makes the appearance significantly different.\n\n/cc @simonricoo ",
